create single cluster 
kind create cluster --name cluster1 --image kindest/node:v1.30.0@sha256:047357ac0cfea04663786a612ba1eaba9702

To get the images
https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/kind/releases

create multi node cluster
kind create cluster --name cluster2 --image kindest/node:v1.30.0@sha256:047357ac0cfea04663786a612ba1eaba9702bef25227a794b52890dd8bcd692e --config=config.yaml

to check list of clusters  
kind get clusters

TO get list of clusters using kubectl with details
 
To switch from one cluster to another cluster.
kubectl config use-context kind-cluster1

To delete the cluster 
kind delete cluster --name cluster2

To list the context
kubectl config get-contexts

To check control plan resource health
kubectl get componentstatus






